<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>蜗牛 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E8%9C%97%E7%89%9B/</link><description>Recent content in 蜗牛 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2025 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2011 13:34:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E8%9C%97%E7%89%9B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><follow_challenge><feedId>42331815237783556</feedId><userId>41909911558319104</userId></follow_challenge><item><title>论中西文化</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/chinese-and-western-culture/</link><pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2011 13:34:36 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/chinese-and-western-culture/</guid><description>中西文化碰撞日益加剧，西方文化如空调般直观实用，易学易用，深受年轻人追捧。中国文化则似扇子，看似笨拙却蕴含深厚底蕴，需用心体悟方能领略其妙处。市井生活中无处不在的传统智慧虽不张扬，却已融入血脉无法剥离。享受现代便利的同时，不妨静心品味扇面墨香里的千年哲思。真正的文化传承在于心静自然凉的境界。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/chinese-and-western-culture/featured.png"/></item><item><title>去年今日</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/lastxmas/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2010 12:25:22 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/lastxmas/</guid><description>悲伤并非季节限定，却总在相似时节反复浮现。去年今日曾在绍兴梅山桥顶风群发圣诞祝福，暗自将生命押注于回复速度，而今通讯录仅剩四人却再无问候。当时寒意中的温暖与如今的沉默形成反差，生活重压让人学会将情绪深埋。成长教会我们以达观面对考验，但请铭记初心与目标。圣诞快乐，缓慢前行的蜗牛！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/lastxmas/featured.png"/></item><item><title>上帝的援助</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/godblessyou/</link><pubDate>Sat, 27 Mar 2010 02:23:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/godblessyou/</guid><description>洪水淹没城市时，神父三次拒绝救援，坚信上帝会亲自拯救，最终溺亡。在天堂质问上帝为何不救他时，上帝回答已派两艘小艇和一架直升机，暗示机会常以平凡形式出现，固执会错失良机！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/godblessyou/featured.png"/></item><item><title>富足的时间 肤浅的生活</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Mar 2010 03:26:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/</guid><description>富足的时间与肤浅的生活交织，未来模糊不清，过往混乱不堪，还有无数擦肩而过的爱情！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/imsnail/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>